text: haey chea karpit nasa puok chomnean moun puokke ban brae ubayokl baokabrasa( anakneasar) bo nde real ubayokl teang lay kuchea kammosetthi robsa a l laoh . trong doeng nouv avei del bokkol krobroub br pru td . haey puok brachheang nung doeng tha tae norna nung ttuol lotthophl chongokraoy da brasaer noh
